trans-unit.source: Represents a declaration for a method of a type.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en deklarering for en metode av en type.

trans-unit.source: CodeMemberMethod can be used to represent the declaration for a method.
trans-unit.target: CodeMemberMethod kan brukes til å representere deklarasjonen for en metode.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod.ReturnType%2A> property specifies the data type of the method's return value.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod.ReturnType%2A>egenskapen angir datatypen for den metoden returverdien.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod.ReturnType%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod.Parameters%2A> property contains the method's parameters.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod.Parameters%2A>egenskapen inneholder den metoden parametere.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod.Parameters%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod.Statements%2A> property contains the statements of the method.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod.Statements%2A>egenskapen inneholder setninger med metoden.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod.Statements%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: This constructor creates an empty <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod> object.
trans-unit.target: Denne konstruktøren oppretter et tomt <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod>objektet.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod>

trans-unit.source: Gets the data types of the interfaces implemented by this method, unless it is a private method implementation, which is indicated by the <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod.PrivateImplementationType*> property.
trans-unit.target: Henter datatypene for grensesnitt implementeres av denne metoden, med mindre det er en privat metodeimplementering, som angis av den <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod.PrivateImplementationType*>egenskapen.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod.PrivateImplementationType*>

trans-unit.source: The types referenced by this collection must consist of interfaces.
trans-unit.target: Typene det henvises til av denne samlingen må bestå av grensesnitt.

trans-unit.source: If this <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod> represents a declaration for a public method, and this method implements a method on an interface, the interface or interfaces this method implements a method of should be referenced in this collection.
trans-unit.target: Hvis <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod>representerer en deklarasjon for en offentlig metode, og denne metoden implementerer en metode i et grensesnitt, eller den grensesnitt denne metoden implementerer en metode for skal refereres til i denne samlingen.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod>

trans-unit.source: The method should still have the same name as the method of the interface that is implemented by this method.
trans-unit.target: Metoden skal fremdeles ha samme navn som metoden grensesnittet implementeres av denne metoden.

trans-unit.source: For some languages, like C#, this has no effect on the syntax.
trans-unit.target: Dette har ingen innvirkning på syntaksen for noen språk som C#.

trans-unit.source: For others, like Visual Basic, there is a special syntax for implementing interfaces.
trans-unit.target: For andre er som Visual Basic det en spesiell syntaks for å implementere grensesnitt.

trans-unit.source: If the method is privately implementing a single interface, the <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod.PrivateImplementationType%2A> property should be used instead.
trans-unit.target: Hvis metoden privat implementerer ett enkelt grensesnitt den <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod.PrivateImplementationType%2A>egenskapen skal brukes i stedet.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod.PrivateImplementationType%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReferenceCollection"></xref> that indicates the interfaces implemented by this method.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReferenceCollection"> </xref> som angir grensesnitt implementeres av denne metoden.

trans-unit.source: Gets the parameter declarations for the method.
trans-unit.target: Henter parameterdeklarasjoner for metoden.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeParameterDeclarationExpressionCollection"></xref> that indicates the method parameters.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeParameterDeclarationExpressionCollection"> </xref> som angir parametrene metoden.

trans-unit.source: An event that will be raised the first time the <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod.ImplementationTypes*> collection is accessed.
trans-unit.target: En hendelse som kan oppstå første gang de <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod.ImplementationTypes*>til samlingen.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod.ImplementationTypes*>

trans-unit.source: To be added.
trans-unit.target: Som skal legges til.

trans-unit.source: An event that will be raised the first time the <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod.Parameters*> collection is accessed.
trans-unit.target: En hendelse som kan oppstå første gang de <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod.Parameters*>til samlingen.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod.Parameters*>

trans-unit.source: To be added.
trans-unit.target: Som skal legges til.

trans-unit.source: An event that will be raised the first time the <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod.Statements*> collection is accessed.
trans-unit.target: En hendelse som kan oppstå første gang de <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod.Statements*>til samlingen.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod.Statements*>

trans-unit.source: To be added.
trans-unit.target: Som skal legges til.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the data type of the interface this method, if private, implements a method of, if any.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir datatypen for grensesnittet denne metoden hvis private, implementerer en metode for, hvis noen.

trans-unit.source: If this <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod> represents the declaration of a private method and the method implements a method of an interface, this property should indicate the interface type that the method is implementing a method of.
trans-unit.target: Hvis <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod>representerer deklarasjon av en privat metode og metoden implementerer en metode for et grensesnitt, denne egenskapen må angi grensesnittype metoden implementerer en metode for å.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod>

trans-unit.source: The type referenced by this property must be an interface.
trans-unit.target: Typen som ble referert av denne egenskapen må være et grensesnitt.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReference"></xref> that indicates the data type of the interface with the method that the private method whose declaration is represented by this <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod"></xref> implements.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReference"> </xref> som angir datatypen for grensesnittet med en metode som metoden private deklarasjon av som representeres av dette <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeMemberMethod"> </xref> implementerer.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the data type of the return value of the method.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir datatypen for returverdien for metoden.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReference"></xref> that indicates the data type of the value returned by the method.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeReference"> </xref> som angir datatypen for verdien som returneres av metoden.

trans-unit.source: Gets the custom attributes of the return type of the method.
trans-unit.target: Henter de egendefinerte attributtene for Returtypen for metoden.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeDeclarationCollection"></xref> that indicates the custom attributes.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeAttributeDeclarationCollection"> </xref> som angir egendefinerte attributter.

trans-unit.source: Gets the statements within the method.
trans-unit.target: Henter setninger i metoden.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeStatementCollection"></xref> that indicates the statements within the method.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeStatementCollection"> </xref> som angir setninger i metoden.

trans-unit.source: Gets the type parameters for the current generic method.
trans-unit.target: Henter de for den gjeldende generisk.

trans-unit.source: A generic method contains one or more unspecified types known as type parameters.
trans-unit.target: En generisk metode inneholder én eller flere uspesifiserte typer kjent som typen parametere.

trans-unit.source: A type parameter name stands for the type within the body of the generic declaration.
trans-unit.target: Et typenavn parameteren står for typen i meldingsteksten generisk-deklarering.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeParameterCollection"></xref> that contains the type parameters for the generic method.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeParameterCollection"> </xref> som inneholder typen parameterne for generell-metoden.
